long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Improve Your Math Skills with this Fun Game!

Numble is a fun daily math game that pushes your mental maths to the limit! Every day, you're presented with a unique challenge for which you have to apply your arithmetics knowledge to solve. Not everyone is smart enough to solve the Numble puzzle... are you up for the challenge?

Numble was created by Arnav Kumar, the lead developer of BlueShift Solutions. You can follow @blueshift.solutions on Instagram to show your support to the developer!
